abstract_ssm: The Papers of Chancellor/Executive Vice President Sidney Borowitz include the materials generated during the years 1972-1977, and also include selected materials created in the Office of Chancellor Allan M. Cartter and elsewhere within the university community dating from as early as 1967. The papers have been divided into twelve series.
